general.desc: BaaS Innovation Co Ltd provides Blockchain solutions and applications. Its core tech has a strong fundamental base from decentralized data processing, data storage on the internet with blockchain tech enhancement, and identity or behavior authentication and authorization. The company expanded to a variety of applications such as Blockchain secured data storage, Blockchain distributed identification as DID, Blockchain Supply Chain Finance, and Web 3.0 transit module.
general.short_desc: IROC Co Ltd, formerly Skymedi Corp designs, markets, and supplies flash memory data storage controllers, digital imaging and audio storage controllers. Its products comprise flash card, USB flash disk, card reader, SSD, eMMC, and bridge controllers.
